{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"简单头部","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Simple_header","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers\">HTTP headers</a>都可以被认为是简单头部：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Accept\"><code>Accept</code></a>,</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Accept-Language\"><code>Accept-Language</code></a>,</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Language\"><code>Content-Language</code></a>,</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Type\"><code>Content-Type</code></a>并且值是 <code>application/x-www-form-urlencoded</code>, <code>multipart/form-data</code>, 或者 <code>text/plain之一的（忽略参数）</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>或者以下客户端头部之一的也可以被认为是简单头部：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/DPR\"><code>DPR</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Downlink\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Downlink (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Save-Data\"><code>Save-Data</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Viewport-Width\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Viewport-Width (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Width\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Width (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>当只包含简单头部时，一个请求则被视为简单请求并且在<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/CORS\">CORS</a>中不需要发送<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Preflight_request\">preflight request</a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"learn_more","title":"Learn more","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers\">HTTP 头部</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Simple_response_header\">Simple response header</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Forbidden_header_name\">Forbidden header name</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Request_header\">Request header</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Learn more","id":"learn_more"}],"summary":"以下的 HTTP headers都可以被认为是简单头部：","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Simple header","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"En-tête simple","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Simple header (単純ヘッダー)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Простой заголовок","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/simple_header","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/simple_header/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Simple_header","title":"简单头部"}],"pageTitle":"简单头部 - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}